{"tid":1420220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美列華為匯率操縱國 內地網民：神仙打架，百姓遭殃","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:04:32.000Z","uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8f7476dc30544ca414b114e6e64776cb9269c9e1","tid":1420220,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190806/large/1565054546_8797.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190806%2Flarge%2F1565054546_8797.jpg&h=c467f1a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中美貿易戰進一步升溫，繼中國相關企業暫停採購美國農產品後，美國財長姆欽（Steven Mnuchin）周一突然發表聲明，將中國列為匯率操縱國，是1994年來首次。<br />\n<br />\n兩國「短兵相接」，內地網民就「中國被指為匯率操縱國」議論紛紛。不少人繼續要無懼貿易戰，直言要中國政府打出「稀土牌」或「美債牌」，不過有網民認為「貿易戰升級至金融戰」、「受苦都是老百姓」、「神仙打架，百姓遭殃」。<br />\n<br />\n流淡定：稀土牌，美債牌還出不出？人家快報雙了<br />\n歌者2向箔：開始掀桌子了！<br />\n理金倉：貿易戰升級到金融戰<br />\nycyy6473：叫口號有甚麼用，最後埋單和承受苦難的還是大眾百姓！<br />\n選一個名字：的確是一場長期戰爭。<br />\n周小林on：冬天來了<br />\n看透人性才能擁有一切：現在真的可以說是內憂外患吶，希望這屆能挺過去<br />\n風中的廠長：變成匯率操縱國標誌着毛衣戰（貿易戰）升級，繼續做好最壞打算吧<br />\n一點趨勢：神仙打架，百姓遭殃<br />\n新浪微博<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190806/59901971?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3AlpYaJO5fXrenGl8f675E3TdSyhZjFTjKrI54ZPlqOaYWkqRg1mgENmE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190806%2F59901971%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3AlpYaJO5fXrenGl8f675E3TdSyhZjFTjKrI54ZPlqOaYWkqRg1mgENmE&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=d3f2df38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190806%2F59901971%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%